metadata.name: NPC
metadata.description:
NPCs have invaded the world!  
Please mint three of them and burn them to summon 1x P3P3, the only one who can save this world!  
JOIN THE FIGHT AGAINST NPCs!

Only an army of P3P3s can save our world's society!

*Mint and burn 3x NPCs to summon 1x P3P3!*

The more NPCs you burn, the more P3P3s you can summon and the bigger your P3P3 army will become!

To save the world you must burn 3x NPCs to summon P3P3, our superhero!
